679
00:40:15,108 --> 00:40:17,691
- It's the thought that counts.

680
00:40:18,571 --> 00:40:19,404
You okay?

681
00:40:22,201 --> 00:40:23,034
- No.

682
00:40:30,215 --> 00:40:31,548
- What happened.

683
00:40:32,909 --> 00:40:36,002
- Paul wants to go to Paris.

684
00:40:36,002 --> 00:40:38,335
