686
00:40:44,907 --> 00:40:46,907
I don't know what I see.

687
00:40:49,337 --> 00:40:52,981
Last night, I dreamt that
I shot him in the head,

688
00:40:52,981 --> 00:40:56,148
then watched him die right in my arms.

689
00:40:58,739 --> 00:41:02,852
