697
00:41:30,048 --> 00:41:32,215
- I don't think you would.

698
00:41:33,821 --> 00:41:35,557
- I'm selfish.

699
00:41:35,557 --> 00:41:36,390
- How?

700
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:40,170
- It just doesn't make any sense.

701
00:41:42,733 --> 00:41:45,983
