709
00:42:13,635 --> 00:42:17,135
Everything about them gives you a hard-on.

710
00:42:20,936 --> 00:42:25,019
You always wanna know
exactly what they're doing.

711
00:42:26,313 --> 00:42:28,380
Nothing else matters.

712
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:29,213
- Yeah.

713
00:42:30,870 --> 00:42:32,391
- [Kurt] It's that spark.

714
00:42:32,391 --> 00:42:35,284
