00:43:58,285 --> 00:44:00,877
- It was right on your screen, Kurt.

735
00:44:00,877 --> 00:44:02,627
- [Kurt] It can wait.

736
00:44:04,110 --> 00:44:06,403
- Seemed pretty urgent.

737
00:44:06,403 --> 00:44:08,826
- It's just weed, babe, it can wait.

738
00:44:08,826 --> 00:44:10,601
