the dots here, what...?

798
00:47:19,729 --> 00:47:22,944
- Just, I need to be alone, all right?

799
00:47:22,944 --> 00:47:23,925
- [Paul] You need space?

800
00:47:23,925 --> 00:47:24,758
- Yeah.

